    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1925-10-30T13:35:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1925-10-30T13:35:00-05:00" n="539"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d539">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">891.00/1368: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Persia</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Amory</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Paraphrase]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Teheran</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1925-10-30T22:00:00+03:25">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 30, 1925—10 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received October 30—4:57 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>75. Demonstrations against Kajar dynasty, which have appearance of spontaneity …
                    have become more wide and frequent. … Course of events may make more difficult
                    position of the American financial advisers.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Amory</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
